index.html
   │
   ▼
main.js
   │
   ├── imports / uses
   │
   ├── game.js  ← creates & runs game instance
   │      │
   │      ├── uses / calls
   │      │
   │      ├── /core
   │      │     ├── controller.js   ← manages game loop, calls gameLogic updates & inputLogic
   │      │     ├── gameLogic.js    ← updates game state (player, enemies, collisions)
   │      │     └── inputLogic.js   ← reads & processes user input
   │      │
   │      ├── /render
   │      │     ├── renderer.js      ← draws the frame, calls spriteRenderer
   │      │     └── spriteRenderer.js  ← draws specific sprites/animations
   │      │
   │      ├── /objects
   │      │     └── game-objects.js  ← defines base & child game entities
   │      │
   │      └── /utils
   │            └── helpers.js      ← utility functions (collision check, math, etc)
   │
/assets
   ├── /sprites  ← images used by renderer/spriteRenderer
   ├── /sounds   ← audio assets (future)
   └── /data     ← JSON/config files for game levels
/css
   └── styles.css  ← linked in index.html
/tests
   └── gameLogic.test.js  ← test core logic (optional)
